WHO   — Duncan Idaho — the swordmaster reborn across the ages
WHAT  — The Atreides swordmaster and one of the finest blades in the Imperium, reborn again and again as a Tleilaxu ghola.
WHERE — D1 · Dune  Framework inputs: House Atreides — the swordmaster across the saga's five thousand years  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
